# Plugforge gm.md Validation Enforcement Enhancement
## PRD - 2026-03-04

Scope: Strengthen agent discipline for validation testing. Add explicit enforcement for agent-browser testing (UI changes) and CLI folder execution (CLI tools). Eliminate skipped verification steps.

**Objective**: Every agent change must be tested BEFORE and AFTER file modification using both plugin:gm:dev (code logic) and agent-browser (UI workflows) where applicable.

